cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SE, cs.SY, cs.PF

The paper discusses the modeling and simulation of Cloud computing environments, which falls under the category of Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC). It also mentions the importance of considering network infrastructure (cs.NI) and software engineering (cs.SE) aspects in Cloud computing. The paper also discusses the need for automatic scaling of applications, which falls under the category of control systems (cs.SY). Finally, the paper mentions the need for policies for migration of VMs for reliability, which falls under the category of performance analysis (cs.PF).
